properties.areaDesc: Guam Coastal Waters; Tinian Coastal Waters; Saipan Coastal Waters; Rota Coastal Waters
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 20 at 4:56PM ChST until January 25 at 6:00PM ChST by NWS Tiyan GU
properties.description:
...STRENGTHENING WINDS AND BUILDING SEAS THIS WEEK...

.FRESH TO STRONG NORTHEAST WINDS WILL DEVELOP ACROSS THE REGION
BEGINNING EARLY TUESDAY. IN ADDITION...SEAS WILL GRADUALLY BUILD
TO HAZARDOUS LEVELS OF AT LEAST 10 FEET FROM THE COMBINATION OF AN
EAST AND A LONG-PERIOD NORTH SWELL.

* WHAT...NORTHEAST WINDS OF 15 TO 20 KT WILL INCREASE TO BETWEEN
15 AND 25 KT FOR MOST OF THE WEEK. SEAS WILL BUILD TO BETWEEN
8 AND 10 FT BY TUESDAY AND CONTINUE THROUGH THE WEEK.

* WHEN...FROM TUESDAY MORNING THROUGH SATURDAY AFTERNOON.

* IMPACTS...SMALL CRAFT CAN BE BLOWN OFF COURSE OR BE CAPSIZED.
properties.instruction:
INEXPERIENCED MARINERS...ESPECIALLY THOSE OPERATING SMALLER
VESSELS...SHOULD AVOID SAILING IN THESE CONDITIONS.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM TUESDAY MORNING THROUGH SATURDAY AFTERNOON
